[SN]TITLE[SN]
Teenage girl critical after Armagh crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A teenage girl is in a critical condition after being airlifted to hospital following a crash in Armagh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It happened on the Monaghan Road. The road is closed between its junctions with Umgola Road and Baltarran Road.
A spokesman for the Northern Ireland Ambulance Service said the girl was airlifted to the Royal Victoria Hospital in Belfast.
